snippet.title: SOULCALIBUR II HD Online - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Soul Still Burns.

SOULCALIBUR II HD Online is available now on Xbox Live and the PlayStation Network!

-Updated HD Graphics.
-Online Multi-player support.
-Featuring Exclusive Characters SPAWN and HEIHACHI

Download now!
PSN: http://bit.ly/17O0riC
Xbox Live: http://bit.ly/17qXkjG
